The policy applied to the target S3 bucket reads the principal from a Systems Manager parameter called s3-logging-iam-role.
This allows the IAM role to be set globally, outside the template.

div.div:
The S3ServerAccessLogTarget output variable is exported and made available to other CloudFormation templates that create S3 buckets.
The log bucket can then be referenced when configuring logging in the new bucket.
